Title: CFBE RPF
Extraction_Protocol: Total RNA was extracted using TRIzol reagent (Invitrogen) and the sample was enriched in mRNA using the Ribo-Zero Gold rRNA Removal Kit (Illumina) and spiked with ERCC RNA Spike-In Mix(Thermo Fisher). RNA-size selection and generation of the cDNA libraries was performed as described {Ingolia, 2009}
